data.description: The existing cozy cottage-style home, although small, is brimming with potential and has a brand new roof and 1 year old AC unit. Perfect for first-time homeowners, downsizers, or those seeking a tranquil retreat. It's a blank slate waiting for your personal touch and doesn't require flood insurance.    OR...for those wanting to build, tear it down and create the home you've always dreamed of, tailored to your specific needs. With such a deep oversized lot (50x165), you can enjoy the luxury of space and customization.  Nestled near MacDill Air Force Base, Bayshore Blvd, Tampa Airport, Crosstown, and with schools, parks, shopping, and dining options within easy reach, you'll have the world at your doorstep.     This area of South Tampa is booming with new construction with a $1M+ price tag. Get in on the action as the neighbors have already started.
